15e5dafe634245e0bb677ab3a","tid":84451,"uid":25302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>prophylactic antibiotic for 你immune 差果時   等你唔好比病菌乘虛而入  病多兩錢用  <br />\n<br />\nbtw  傷風- 病毒引起  感冒- 細菌引起  要分清楚</blockquote><br />\n感冒- 細菌引起 <br />\n流行性感冒=細菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7462013d550f3a5fabe6e387a857f243c74e765f","tid":84451,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:06:05.000Z","msg":"因為唔係醫藥分家，醫生開多隻藥就收你多d<br />\n有d 醫生就係要賺多少少錢就是但開俾你<br />\n<br />\n但有d 好老既醫生仲停係抗生素殺咩都ok 既層面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d9f77a29f84ceddf94b0fe5f753dae11df0d1b","tid":84451,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:11:27.000Z","msg":"因為病毒只係一堆蛋白質，定義唔到佢有冇生命，病毒只係依附喺體細胞上面，然後植入自己嘅蛋白質，令體細胞病變<br />\n<br />\n唔同細菌，細菌只係依靠體細胞繁殖，中間要靠細胞膜嘅受質將自己嘅遺傳物質傳入體細胞，從而操控細胞核為自己繁殖<br />\n<br />\n抗生素係用來針對細菌呢種特性，對病毒冇效<br />\n<br />\n頭盔：自學所知，有錯請屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb24a219ed098878e1176b132f9b230143b37ef9","tid":84451,"uid":35649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"你估佢地真係分到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到你tonsil有白色珍珠 咪開劑board spectrum antibiotic比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好嚴重既感冒通常會同你做過quick test既(撩你個鼻) 之後咪比d特效咁"}]}